cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.HC 

This paper focuses on the automatic extraction of persons and their attributes from photo albums using convolutional neural networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia). Additionally, the paper discusses the efficiency of the proposed approach, which could be relevant to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper deals with organizing photo albums, which could be related to cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction).
